searchFormContent:
<el-form-item label="登录ID">
<el-input size=medium v-model="rabbitUserListsearchFormModel.loginid.value" placeholder="登录ID"></el-input>
</el-form-item>
<el-form-item label="姓名">
<el-input size=mini v-model="rabbitUserListsearchFormModel.realName.value" placeholder="姓名"></el-input>
</el-form-item>
<el-form-item label="电话">
<el-input size=mini v-model="rabbitUserListsearchFormModel.phone.value" placeholder="电话"></el-input>
</el-form-item>
<el-form-item label="出生日期">
<el-input size=small v-model="rabbitUserListsearchFormModel.birthday.value" placeholder="出生日期"></el-input>
</el-form-item>
